- **Update Usage**: Pass `perfectDayLog` to [calculatePerfectDays](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/utils.js#60-77).

#### [MODIFY] [Stats.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/스위치웹서비스/daily-habit-tracker/src/Stats.jsx)
- **Update Props**: Accept `perfectDayLog`.
- **Update Usage**: Pass `perfectDayLog` to [calculatePerfectDays](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/utils.js#60-77) (if applicable, though Stats usually calculates per-habit. I'll check if it displays global perfect days).

## Verification Plan
### Manual Verification
1.  **Achieve Perfect Day**: Check off all habits for today.
2.  **Verify Count**: Check Profile, note "Perfect Days" count (e.g., 5).
3.  **Reset Day**: Click "Reset Day" on Dashboard.
4.  **Verify Count Persists**: Check Profile again. The count should **still be 5**, not 4.
5.  **Re-complete Habits**: Check off habits again.
6.  **Verify Count Stability**: The count should remain 5 (not increase to 6 for the same day).
